name: City of Stars Tee
description:

description:

name: The Eclectic Snapback
description:
"The Eclectic"
This painter's cap snapback features embroidered designs, a unique retro shape, adjustable plastic snapback, and a hand-sewn button to set you apart from the pack. For the cap-lover that doesn't want to be the one to jump on the snapback bandwagon late, but the one pulling the damn cart.

The back will feature the TYA signature woven label with a unique function that we will keep under wraps for now.

AVAILABLE FOR PRE-ORDER WITH NO SHIPPING FEE.

Comes with a free sticker and a randomly selected pin. 
Shipping within Canada costs $8 but is free for purchases over $50.
